


$ touch ~/.vimrc	(vundle file)

 i  = INSERT MODE
esc = COMMAND MODE

in command mode press  :


:ls -> list all buffers (recently open still loaded files)
:b <Buffer numbre> / :b <Buffer name> (Autocomplete)


:sp <filename>  split the screen horizontal
:vs <filename>  split screen vertical
:q   	quit
:q!	quit forced, scrap all changes
:w	write (save)
:wq	write (save) and quit

Navigate between Screens - Hold CTRL + (HJKL)
H -> left 
L -> Right 
J -> Up 
K -> Down
